    <p class="mb-4">
      The daily drawdown is balance-based and calculated from the previous day's balance snapshot. If the limit is exceeded on equity, the account breaches. The standard profit split is <strong>80%</strong>, with <strong>90%</strong> available only through the paid profit split add-on.
    </p>

