    </p>
    <p class="mb-4">
      You can only run one Day Trader challenge at a time, and there's a single instrument profit cap of 75% of the target to stop the challenge from turning into a single lucky entry. Day Trader challenges can be traded on <strong>MT5, MT4, or TradeLocker</strong>.
